<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 15:15:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着“发脾气”的到来，全球投资者因债券市场抛售而感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/global-markets-yields-2025-01-08/</link><description>全球一些最大政府债券市场的大幅抛售和美元飙升正在给金融市场带来冲击波，随着唐纳德·特朗普政策的不确定性加剧，痛苦加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 14:54:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/global-markets-yields-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>尽管经济低迷，中国预计新年旅游人数将会增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expects-increase-new-year-travel-numbers-despite-economic-doldrums-2025-01-08/</link><description>中国预计参加即将到来的农历新年旅游热潮的人数将会增加，尽管经济不景气，但当局估计在为期 40 天的庆祝活动期间，国内旅游人数将达到创纪录的 90 亿人次。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expects-increase-new-year-travel-numbers-despite-economic-doldrums-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：债券呈红色闪烁，“期限溢价”处于 10 年高位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>圭亚那石油出口猛增，2024年获得欧洲市场份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/guyana-oil-exports-jump-gain-europe-market-share-2024-2025-01-08/</link><description>根据贸易商和金融公司 LSEG 的航运数据，圭亚那的石油出口量去年增长了 54%，达到约 582,000 桶/日，这得益于欧洲炼油厂对易于加工的低硫原油的需求，以取代一些中东等级原油。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/guyana-oil-exports-jump-gain-europe-market-share-2024-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着最高法院诉讼的临近，TikTok 的命运使特朗普和共和党同僚产生分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktoks-fate-divides-trump-fellow-republicans-supreme-court-action-looms-2025-01-08/</link><description>尽管特朗普要求最高法院阻止美国即将实施的对 TikTok 的禁令，但他的许多共和党盟友却提出了相反的要求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktoks-fate-divides-trump-fellow-republicans-supreme-court-action-looms-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国黄河源头附近发生5.5级地震</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/magnitude-55-earthquake-strikes-china-near-source-yellow-river-2025-01-08/</link><description>自周二以来，广阔的青藏高原一直受到地震活动的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 08:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/magnitude-55-earthquake-strikes-china-near-source-yellow-river-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：与中国有联系的船东否认台湾有关破坏海底电缆的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-linked-shipowner-denies-taiwan-accusation-damaging-undersea-cable-2025-01-08/</link><description>台湾一家公司的船只涉嫌损坏海底通讯电缆，该公司的中国董事周三表示，没有证据表明这艘船参与其中，这一事件引起了台北政府的警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 08:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-linked-shipowner-denies-taiwan-accusation-damaging-undersea-cable-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>女子亚冠联赛浦和抽签对阵武汉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/urawa-drawn-meet-wuhan-womens-asian-champions-league-2025-01-08/</link><description>周三在吉隆坡举行首届亚洲女子冠军联赛八强抽签仪式后，卫冕洲际冠军浦和红钻队将在三月份的亚洲女子冠军联赛四分之一决赛中对阵中国武汉江大队。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 07:54:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/urawa-drawn-meet-wuhan-womens-asian-champions-league-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>加关税？市场感受到特朗普关税风险带来的最大压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-trump-tariffs-graphic-2025-01-08/</link><description>从中国到欧洲，从加拿大到墨西哥，唐纳德·特朗普承诺在不到两周内就任美国总统时提高关税，这已经让世界市场感到震惊。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 05:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-trump-tariffs-graphic-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪称5000辆新能源汽车启航欧洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-says-5000-nevs-set-sail-europe-2025-01-08/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪周三表示，第三艘载着近5000辆新能源汽车开往欧洲的滚装船已起航。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 03:52:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-says-5000-nevs-set-sail-europe-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国扩大消费者以旧换新计划以重振经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-scope-consumer-trade-ins-home-appliances-2025-01-08/</link><description>中国在消费者以旧换新计划中增加了更多家用电器产品，并将在今年为更多数字产品提供补贴，以重振低迷的家居行业的需求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 03:12:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-scope-consumer-trade-ins-home-appliances-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>迪士尼开发情感经济，粉红狐狸“莉娜贝尔”赢得中国人心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pink-fox-linabell-wins-chinese-hearts-disney-taps-emotional-economy-2025-01-08/</link><description>每周，只要营销工作一有空，艾达·贾就会在上海迪士尼乐园排队几个小时，只为与一只长着蓝色大眼睛的毛茸茸的粉色狐狸莉娜贝尔共度几分钟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 01:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pink-fox-linabell-wins-chinese-hearts-disney-taps-emotional-economy-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：检查员称比亚迪以非正规签证将数百名中国工人带到巴西</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/byd-brought-hundreds-chinese-workers-brazil-irregular-visas-inspector-2025-01-08/</link><description>一位重要的劳工监察员告诉路透社，电动汽车生产商比亚迪带着数百名持非正常签证的中国工人在巴西建造一家工厂，并补充说该公司已承诺对留在该国的工人遵守当地劳动法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/byd-brought-hundreds-chinese-workers-brazil-irregular-visas-inspector-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>西藏地震幸存者搜寻工作日益紧迫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rescue-efforts-under-way-after-earthquake-tibet-kills-more-than-120-2025-01-08/</link><description>中国官员表示，西藏地震灾区已有400多名被困在废墟中的人获救，喜马拉雅山麓发生强烈地震后的第二天，天寒地冻，仍有不明人数下落不明。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rescue-efforts-under-way-after-earthquake-tibet-kills-more-than-120-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿对中国宁德时代的标签可能会对特斯拉产生怎样的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-washingtons-tag-chinas-catl-could-affect-tesla-2025-01-07/</link><description>华盛顿将宁德时代列入与中国军方合作的公司名单，这可能会让特斯拉创始人埃隆·马斯克陷入困境，挑战他如何平衡自己在特朗普政府中的角色与与中国的关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 23:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-washingtons-tag-chinas-catl-could-affect-tesla-2025-01-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>